## Harness dependencies (checks)

Installed separately; the CLI treats a missing binary as `skip`, not
`fail`:

- `yamllint` — static YAML hygiene
- `helm` — chart lint, dry-run, template rendering
- `kubeconform` — k8s API schema validation
- `trivy` — chart config scan (optional)
- `gitleaks` — secret scanning (optional)
- `hadolint` — Dockerfile lint
- `docker`, `kubectl` — only called by the harness CLI

